While Denzu was walking into the forest he thought about things and got 
angry. Why didn't his own kind, after all his time looking for them, rejected 
him, he went to bot mode and thrust his fist into a nearby hill, the entire 
top of the hill crumbles a way. HE notices something, a piece of metal, he 
uncovers it to reveal a Stasus POD, he continues to dig to check for anything 
else.
